Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,來得正好 我們整理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 西蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,難道妳今天叫我們來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想向你們報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,前陣子我們去過的遺跡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是我叔叔 奇斯葛裡夫留下的筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔既是煉金術士 同時也是一名研究者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他周遊各地遺跡進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有時也會破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好像這也是他的信條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 已經被中央通緝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得 好像在哪聽說過一個類似的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個筆記本裡寫著的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,關於遺跡的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在解讀過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞭解了許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那個遺跡裡的壁畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是解明在我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舊時代的人們為何走向滅亡的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說 是有著高度煉金術的文明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有說法認為他們是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,資源的枯竭與爭奪而自取滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但這裡描繪的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,諸多國家齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,共建遺跡的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 在這個遺跡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,進行著在乾涸的大地植樹造林的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,精誠合作植樹造林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼讚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 舊時代的人們走向了滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有如此高度文明的人們同舟共濟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,結果卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔想向我說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是人類過去走向了怎樣的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,以及我們接下來該走向何方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我還想掌握更多信息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,關於那些尚無人涉足的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,未踏遺跡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那兒還是一方淨土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會有新發現的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的夢想就是踏上那座遺跡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我找過不少石板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想把它拼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也跟未踏遺跡很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在未踏遺跡上有個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這代表什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要踏上那個遺跡 或許就能得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我向開發班提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,調查未踏遺跡的正式提案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,請交給瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我接到了西蕾雅的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始緊急會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家到齊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,開門見山地說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才接到了中央的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,下季度中央將向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們柯爾賽特派遣未踏遺跡調查隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,中央派來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來我們會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,柯爾賽特支部會加入到調查隊中嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有接到關於我們是否會參與調查的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的工作是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在調查隊到來之前保護遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,以及 確保接近遺跡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是…就把我們當馬前卒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,稍後我會做出具體指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,會議結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今日就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就當個中央的馬前卒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要我們柯爾賽特支部有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 剛才掉到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是愛絲卡要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要避雨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杜克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看到愛絲卡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 剛才走到那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看到愛絲卡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 愛絲卡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼跑到這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,突然 想要看看這邊的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:09:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 好像什麼都看不見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡 自從媽媽米莉亞去世以來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,變得經常 遠眺那個遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 會對未踏遺跡產生興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能聽見什麼聲音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒有 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡一直說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有人住在 那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,對於年幼的那孩子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽米莉亞 就在那 未踏遺跡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,或許當成了這樣一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 她應該不會 到現在還相信著這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 愛絲卡至今
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,仍然心懷去到那裡的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 凝望著未踏遺跡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿孩童那般閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,胸懷夢想 方能閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我從小懷著的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想有一天 能到那個遺跡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那一刻 我第一次感到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,自己與愛絲卡之間有了些許接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是羅吉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 這次？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是來說這件事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,西蕾雅遞交的未踏遺跡調查委託函
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就把這個受理了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們搶先去未踏遺跡調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不～行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,中央已經下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要求遺跡調查須待中央調查隊到來後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,方可進行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,未踏遺跡的調查委託肯定是不能受理的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等… 你們也？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓愛絲卡打起精神來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為這是個好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才連薇爾貝爾和妮歐都跑到我這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還批我說愛絲卡發燒都是我的錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為她的夢想不能想想辦法嗎什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,囉哩囉唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她們以為老娘就好受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,寫完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,寫完了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,向中央提交的工作申請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們開發班為迎接中央調查隊的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,組織進行保護遺跡工作 並確保接近其的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就是照章執行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不過是個馬前卒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,字面上看是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我們會扎扎實實地工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,包括字面以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,確保接近遺跡的方法是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為了開發接近遺跡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接近遺跡也沒關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,並且 為了保護遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要進入遺跡內部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,弄清有哪些保護對象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 在中央的傢伙到來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們柯爾賽特支部自己也能調查遺跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,搶在中央之前下手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,明明你們前陣子還是中央的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,確 確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我從前也想有朝一日能升遷到中央呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我早就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也不曾後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我們開發班要搶在中央前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,調查未踏遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 稍微有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天妳不是請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不過燒也退了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長去吃午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出勤記錄就由我來受理了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,開發班裡也沒人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那個計劃最大的難關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個支部長了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 聽說那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是討伐班裡勇猛無雙的獵手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是我的前輩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算交上剛剛那份申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也不可能騙過他那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,既有基層工作經驗又讀得懂申請書的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的目的是逃不過他的眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就等於
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個方案不可能了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天 不管瑪麗恩班長怎麼反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長都不為所動不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事情不試試怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請受理這份文件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,工作申請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,寫得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳寫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話中央也會通過的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然索爾大概會吐槽兩句預算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我去做做工作的話應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就算交上這份申請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們參加到調查之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等之後中央的傢伙來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不也就都會暴露的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 我們也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是愛絲卡能去遺跡調查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她的夢想就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這之後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最壞的結果 整個柯爾賽特支部都要被解散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,中央那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我會申請讓我們盡可能地參與進調查之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,解散就解散了 支部什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,杜克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,杜克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,柯爾賽特支部本來是為什麼設立的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了調查未踏遺跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,調查未踏遺跡 是我們全支部的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不能實現這份願景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,徒留一個支部又有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,支部也是維持柯爾賽特這座城市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,維持城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼奇怪的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這還不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在維持一個城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你老糊塗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是一直向著夢想勇往直前的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還在討伐班混的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,每每打倒怪物 我們都要把酒敘夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真想去未踏遺跡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要有怪物的話跟它們打打看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面會有些什麼傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要使些什麼武器才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上都是赤條條的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,裸聊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誤會！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒裸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是這傢伙把我灌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而且借著酒勁 每天晚上都要帶妹子回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呀——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,給我住口 杜克！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你肌肉都萎縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是現役
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不像你早早就退出一線了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐辦公室坐傻了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是 瞧你腿都在抖了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,班 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,店要被砸壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡 快阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就算在下恐怕也有點為難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,亞文 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那可是怪獸大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你這滿身橫肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在歲月面前也一樣一天天衰頹下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是連腦子都老朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杜克 支部長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 咱們多久沒這樣鬧過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事嗎 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老大才是完全沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 什麼都沒變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 就算支部解散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再找個地方去混討伐班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 你要想幹的話 我奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這份申請 我會交到中央去的 瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是說 支部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,管它是未踏遺跡還是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想去哪兒就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想調查哪兒就調查哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我都給妳頂著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,未踏…遺跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以去未踏遺跡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒問題了哦 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是瑪麗恩班長想到的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我一個人的功勞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也多虧了羅吉向支部長進言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不…我…只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不…我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝…各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,說了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:22:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要…人類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界不需要人類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,飛揚浮躁 背叛 欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,光說不練 優柔寡斷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一意孤行 偎慵墮懶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人類實在太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不需要人類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:32.59,Default,,0,0,12,,不要放棄！
